<img src="http://c.biz-file.com/c/1801/426984.jpg" alt="Exxaro and DRA to build Belfast Implementation Project" width="625" height="417">© Lubos Chlubny – 123RF.comThe coal handling and preparation plant consists of primary and secondary sizing stations, overland conveyor, two 7500t silos, low gravity and high gravity Dense Medium Separation (DMS) modules, thickener circuit, filter plant,  stacker conveyor. The plant will produce both a domestic and an export product. The project will commence in January 2018 and is expected to be completed in October 2019.